     <div type="encomium">
   <head>The Bookes request.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>MY sute (good Reader) is but small,</l>
      <l>and such, as I am sure</l>
      <l>Your courtesies on my behalfe</l>
      <l>may easily procure.</l>
      <l>Your fauour is the thing I aske:</l>
      <l>and nothing else I craue:</l>
      <l>For that in l<gap reason="illegible" resp="#apex" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>e of traueyle done,</l>
      <l>
         <hi>Hyll</hi> (onely) sée<gap reason="illegible" resp="#apex" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>th to haue.</l>
      <l>A recompence sufficeing well,</l>
      <l>and counteruayling aye,</l>
      <l>The blacke reproch that <hi>Momus</hi> tongue</l>
      <l>enforceth day by daye.</l>
      <l>To learned sort I onely sue:</l>
      <l>I force not <hi>Momus</hi> ne <hi>Zoylus</hi> crue.</l>
   </lg>
</div>
